data.title: Norodom Sihanouk (King of Cambodia)
data.meta_description: Profile of king of cambodia Norodom Sihanouk featuring biographical facts, historical events and details of Norodom Sihanouk's personal life.
data.text:
Norodom Sihanouk

Profession: King of Cambodia

Biography: Cambodian leader who was King, Prime Minister and President of his country

Born: October 31, 1922

Birthplace: Phnom Penh, Cambodia

Generation: Greatest Generation

Chinese Zodiac: Dog

Star Sign: Scorpio

Died: October 15, 2012 (aged 89)

Cause of Death: Heart attack

Historical Events

Cambodian Prince Norodom Sihanouk returns to Phnom Penh after thirteen years of exile

Norodom Sihanouk again installed as King of Cambodia

King Norodom Sihanouk of Cambodia abdicates

Personal Life

Cambodia king Norodom Sihanouk (29) weds Paule Monique Izzi
